RENEW Program by StarHub
StarHub initiated a massive consumer-oriented environmental program which provides consumers with avenues to recycle their electronic waste. StarHub (n.d.) identified suitable locations for having a RENEW bin, and engaged a supplier to produce and provide bins to these locations. The electronic waste conveniently. After one year, StarHub (n.d.) declares that they have collected 23 tons of electronic waste from consumers, it is limited to small and medium sized enterprises (SMEs). In other words, it is not applicable for individuals, mini-scale companies and large companies. Thus, it partly meets the first criterion but fails regarding the second criterion either.
